fr.lirmm.graphik.util

Class Partition<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.lirmm.graphik.util.Partition<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<ArrayList<E>>

    public class Partition<E>
extends Object
implements Iterable<ArrayList<E>>
    A partition of terms. A partition can be associated with a substition : two terms are in the same class if one is the image of the other ex: the partition associated with {(a,b)(c,b)(d,e)(e,f)} is {{a,b,c}{d,e,f}}

      Return the join of this and the given partition p the join of two partition is obtained by making the union of their non-disjoint classes until stability ex: the join of {{a,b,c},{d,e}} and {{e,g},{k,l}} is {{a,b,c},{d,e,g},{k,l}}
